Three separate recordings, taken over a ~20 minute period. Continuing bird, first found in December. Now in molt, sex is not totally clear. 200 Hz high pass filter used to reduce background noise from distant traffic.

I used iZotope RX de-hum & spectral denoise to eliminate some noise from the road and lawn equipment, an additional HPF @ 450 Hz, normalized the audio to -0.5dB with the Invisible Limiter set with no compression and Sample Rate processing at 192kHz (allowing for some more openness in the recording by allowing those higher frequencies to pass).
